*:[[Rhymes:English:-ʌɡ|Rhymes: -ʌɡ]]

===Noun===
'''jug''' (''plural:'' ''[[jugs]]'')

#A large round [[serve|serving]] [[vessel]], with a small [[mouth]], a [[handle]] and often a [[stopper]].
#The [[amount]] that a jug can hold.
#(''slang'') [[jail]] / [[gaol]]
#(''vulgar slang'') (''plural'') A [[woman]]'s [[breast]]s.

